prompts.frontCover:
Flat 2D illustration for a greeting card front. A funny and charming beach scene in a botanical art style.

The scene is set on a sunny, sandy beach with gentle teal waves lapping the shore. A large, whimsical botanical arch frames the top half of the card, composed of lush monstera leaves, vibrant hibiscus flowers, and trailing green vines.

At the center, cartoon illustrated versions of Lao Lao and Jordan from the reference photo are having a comical moment. Lao Lao is laughing joyfully as she tries to balance on a surfboard in the shallow water. Jordan is playfully attempting to push her off the board, a big, mischievous grin on his face. He is wearing a simple brown hoodie and dark shorts. Lao Lao is wearing her light blue sweatshirt and black pants.

Surrounding them are two small, fluffy white dogs wearing tiny floral leis, causing chaotic fun. One dog is gleefully digging in the sand, sending a spray of sand into the air. The other dog is playfully tugging on the leash tied to the back of the surfboard.

In the center of the scene, positioned safely within the botanical arch, the words "Happy Birthday, Lao Lao!" are written in a beautiful, flowing, hand-drawn cursive script in a dark green color.

The overall illustration is bright and cheerful, with a soft, clean aesthetic, combining the botanical elements with a humorous, personalized beach scene.
